&lt;h2 id="free-will">Free Will&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>The laws of physics are wonderful, not least because they show us some of the magic formulas behind the seeming mystery of life and the universe. They are also good and proper ‘laws’ – that is, they are intended to be equivalent across space and time.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>